{
  "id": "adv_bond_rui_01_05",
  "title": "天動瑠依5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "庭の手入れって何をすればいいのかしら\n特に荒れてる感じもしないけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what needs to be done for garden maintenance.\nIt doesn't look particularly messy‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "細かい雑草を抜いてほしい、って言ってました\nどうしても自然と生えてくるみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She asked us to pull out the small weeds.\nThey just seem to grow back naturally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "雑草……よく分からないけれど……\n草を抜いていけばいいのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Weeds… I'm not really sure‚ but…\nI just have to pull the grass‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私もあまり詳しくないんですが\n遙子さんから説明は受けてるので、たぶん大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not an expert either‚\nbut Haruko-san explained it‚ so it should be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。分からないことがあったら琴乃に聞くわね\nそれじゃあ、始めましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. I'll ask you‚ Kotono‚ if I have questions.\nWell then‚ shall we begin?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7133.3333334000035
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ん……なかなか抜けないわね……\nんしょ………………ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… these aren't coming out easily…\nHeave……… phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.733337148,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1599.9961853000002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.3295187
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.662852000001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10066.662852
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "根っこから抜くのって……っ……\n思ったより力がいりますね。時間掛かりそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pulling them from the roots… urgh…\ntakes more strength than I thought. It might take a while…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4000038147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、瑠依さん\n午後からお仕事があるのに、汗かいちゃいそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ Rui-san.\nYou have work this afternoon‚ you'll be all sweaty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9000038147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ。いい準備運動になるわ\nそれに庭のことはずっと遙子さんに任せっきりだったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. It'll be a good warm-up.\nBesides‚ we've always left the garden to Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが忙しい時くらいは、支え合わないと\nここはみんなの寮なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should support each other when she's busy.\nThis is a dorm for all of us‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4000104268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、瑠依さんって意外と熱いところがありますよね\n初めはもっと、クールなイメージでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're unexpectedly passionate‚ Rui-san.\nI thought you had a much cooler image at first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3333437602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "熱いところ……自分では分からないけれど……\n任せてくれた遙子さんの想いには応えたいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Passionate… I don't really see it myself‚ but…\nI want to live up to Haruko-san's trust.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3000104268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "小さな仕事でも、綺麗になった庭を見たら\n遙子さんも、きっとみんなも、喜んでくれるはず",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even with small tasks‚ seeing a clean garden\nwill surely make Haruko-san and everyone happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1666770935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃も汗をかきながら頑張ってるし\n私も負けてられないわ。ふふ、ここからは競争よ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ since you're working so hard too‚ Kotono‚\nI can't afford to lose. Hehe‚ it's a race from now on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9000099182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "競争？　分かりました。どっちが沢山抜けるか……\n……って、瑠依さん！？　待って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A race? Understood. Let's see who pulls more…\n…Wait‚ Rui-san!? Stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8666765849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "待たないわ！\nステージの上じゃ、誰も待ってくれないでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not waiting!\nNo one waits for you on the stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9000099182,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3234151000056
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなくて、今瑠依さんが抜いてるの――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not that! What you're pulling right now――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3000099182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "どんどんいくわよ！\n白い翼で！　世界を翔ける！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm keeping this pace!\nWith white wings! Soar across the world!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3000063578,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.660308899995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.660308899989
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.660308899989
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それ雑草じゃなくて、遙子さんが育ててるお花です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those aren't weeds‚ they're flowers Haruko-san is growing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3666730244,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}